{Speech 2}{}{Buy us a drink, smoothskin.@@Boy, am I thirsty.@@Too good to drink with us?@@Where are my pals, Johnny Stroller and Jim Bean?@@I’ll have mine shaken, not stirred.@@Ask Wooz to tell you a story.@@Let’s sing a song.@@...And then the heads do what? I just don’t understand Wooz.@@What’s an apple?}
{Speech 3}{}{You’re pretty nice for a smoothskin.@@Buy us another round, smoothy.@@How dry I am, How dry I am...@@You’re okay in my book.@@Hey, watch out for the rat.@@I wonder why Skeeter never joins us?@@We’re trying to breed a new type of brahmin - with only one head.@@Somebody ought to start making more clothes here.@@Ahh, beer is good.@@This beer is great. It’s the water -- and a lot more.@@You’re the best smoothskin I’ve ever known.@@More glow-juice! More glow-juice!@@Gives us another, eh smoothy?}
